@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rhozkf(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.exp((v0 + 0.81 / v2 + 0.46)) * 0.64)
    tmp = wp.cos(0.94)
    tmp = 0.37
    v1 = (wp.abs((tmp + 0.55 - v2 + 0.61)) * ((tmp + 0.36 / tmp + 0.99) - wp.sin(v1 + 0.69)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
